        <p>Covid long haulers can experience an array of symptoms long after infection. Scientists and physicians have learned a lot about the myriad ways long Covid can manifest and its potential causes, but there is still much work to be done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="article-container" style="transform: translate3d(0px, 37.6px, 0px);">
      <div class="article-header">
        <div class="eyebrow">
          <a href="/health-disease">Health & Disease</a>
        </div>
        
         <p class="article-info"> <a href="/reset">
          Reset
          </a>
        </p>
        

       
        <h1>Long Covid: A parallel pandemic</h1>
          <p class="article-subhead">
          VIDEO: Tens of millions of people are living with long Covid. Yale immunologist Akiko Iwasaki explains the current state of play in the search for causes of, and treatments for, this potentially debilitating illness.
          </p>

          <p class="article-byline">
              
              <span class="author-byline">By <a href="/action/doSearch?DOResourceTypeId=knowable&sortBy=earliest&startPage=&text1=Hunni Media for Knowable Magazine">Hunni Media for Knowable Magazine</a></span>
            
            
              <span class="pub-date">08.08.2022</span>
            
          </p>

        <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><div class="ember-view"><ul class="social-media-links"><li><a href="#" class="sm-facebook" data-service="facebook" data-locale="en" title="Share on Facebook">Facebook</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-twitter" data-service="twitter" data-locale="en" title="Share on Twitter">Twitter</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-linkedin" data-service="linkedin" data-locale="en" title="Share on LinkedIn">Linkedin</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-reddit" data-service="reddit" data-locale="en" title="Share on Reddit">Reddit</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-flipboard" data-service="flipboard" data-locale="en" title="Share on Flipboard">Flipboard</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-email" data-service="email" data-locale="en" title="Email">Email</a></li><li><a href="#" class="sm-print" data-service="print" data-locale="en" title="Print or save as PDF">Print</a></li></ul></div>
      </div>
      



        <div data-widget-def="general-html-asset" data-widget-id="0a62df66-111f-4e6c-bd92-5888ec7dbd4b">
            <style>
